The paper discusses the security of Industrial Control Systems (ICSs), which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also focuses on providing a low-cost and open-source testbed for education and research, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of ICSs in critical infrastructures, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). Finally, the paper mentions the use of simulation, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL).
